g, Sussex, Inglaterra, United Kingdom, seu pai, William Lovell, tinha 27 anos e sua mãe, Elizabeth St Clere, tinha 30 anos. Ele casou-se com Lady Constance Hussey em 1476, em Harting, Sussex, Inglaterra, United Kingdom. Eles tiveram pelo menos 3 filhas. Ele faleceu em 20 de abril de 1501, em sua cidade natal, com 51 anos, e foi sepultado em South Harting, West Sussex, Inglaterra, United Kingdom."},"ro":{"1450–20 April 1501":"1450–20 aprilie 1501","1450–1501":"1450–1501","1460–1525":"1460–1525","1476–1560":"1476–1560","1478–1560":"1478–1560","1488–1521":"1488–1521","1423–Male":"1423–Decedat","1421–Female":"1421–Decedată","1450":"1450","1560":"1560","1460":"1460","20 April 1501":"20 aprilie 1501","April 1501":"aprilie 1501","1525":"1525","1501":"1501","1478":"1478","1423":"1423","1488":"1488","1521":"1521","1476":"1476","1421":"1421","about 1450":"aproximativ 1450","Parish Church of Saint Mary and Saint Gabriel, South Harting, Chichester district, West Sussex, England, United Kingdom":"South Harting, West Sussex, Anglia, United Kingdom","Sussex, England":"Sussex, Anglia, United Kingdom","Harting, Sussex, England":"Harting, Sussex, England","Harting, Chichester district, West Sussex, England, United Kingdom":"Harting, Sussex, Anglia, United Kingdom"},"ru":{"1450–20 April 1501":"1450 г.–20 апреля 1501 г.","1450–1501":"1450г.–1501г.","1460–1525":"1460г.–1525г.","1476–1560":"1476г.–1560г.","1478–1560":"1478г.–1560г.","1488–1521":"1488г.–1521г.","1423–Male":"1423г.–Умерший","1421–Female":"1421г.–Умершая","1450":"1450 г.","1560":"1560 г.","1460":"1460 г.","20 April 1501":"20 апреля 1501 г.","April 1501":"апрель 1501 г.","1525":"1525 г.","1501":"1501 г.","1478":"1478 г.","1423":"1423 г.","1488":"1488 г.","1521":"1521 г.","1476":"1476 г.","1421":"1421 г.","about 1450":"около 1450 г.","Parish Church of Saint Mary and Saint Gabriel, South Harting, Chichester district, West Sussex, England, United Kingdom":"соут хартинг, вест суссекс, Англия, Великобритания","Sussex, England":"с